OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fdry through the evening and much of
OL,7,Fthe night with largely clear skies.
OL,8,FChance of the odd shower over north
OL,9,FArgyll and the Isles towards morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FDry with some spells of
OL,12,Fsunshine, although some high cloud
OL,13,Faround. A warm day but cooler along
OL,14,Fsoutheastern facing coasts.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,17,Fstart on Wednesday then dry and
OL,18,Fbright. Rain at first on Thursday
OL,19,Ffollowed by a few showers. Rain likely
OL,20,Fon Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
